                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9435" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1417</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1152 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">员工动起来，企业跑起来：日照瑞华阿米巴经营会计的搭建之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Employees move up, the enterprise runs up:Rizhao Ruihua amoeba business accounting construction road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙晶慧，王钰轩，张煜青，汪星宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">日照瑞华新材料科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矿冶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">25 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阿米巴经营；经营会计；单位时间核算</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Amoeba operations; business accounting; unit time accounting</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着中国经济发展进入新常态，企业自身面临的市场环境也日益复杂，企业越来越注重精细化管理，对企业自身的会计建设提出了更高的要求。日照瑞华新材料科技有限公司（简称“日照瑞华”）是一家从事有色冶炼加工为主的中小型制造企业。为了解决粗放式发展导致的经营不善的问题，在公司内部驱动下导入阿米巴经营会计。旨在有效削减产品成本，优化产品质量，并激发员工生产热情，强化企业整体运营效能，进而提升市场竞争力。本案例围绕故事主线详细描述了日照瑞华实施阿米巴经营会计的背景、搭建过程、遇到的挑战及解决措施，并展现了该模式在提升企业竞争力和管理效率上的显著成效，帮助学生理解掌握阿米巴经营会计，同时对想要导入精细化管理中小制造业企业具有借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As China&#39;s economic development has entered the new normal, the market environment facing enterprises themselves is becoming increasingly complex. Enterprises pay more and more attention to fine management, which has put forward higher requirements for their own accounting construction. Rizhao Ruihua New Material Technology Co., LTD. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Rizhao Ruihua&quot;) is a small and medium-sized manufacturing enterprise mainly engaged in non-ferrous smelting and processing. In order to solve the problem of poor management caused by extensive development, the amoeba operating accounting was introduced under the internal drive of the company. It aims to effectively reduce product cost, optimize product quality, stimulate the enthusiasm of employees for production, strengthen the overall operation efficiency of the enterprise, and then enhance the market competitiveness. This case around the story line describes the Rizhao ruihua background of ameba operating accounting, building process, challenges an</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阿米巴经营；经营会计；心理契约理论；信息孤岛</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
